'''Lodash'''是一個[[開源軟件|開放源碼]]的[[JavaScript函式庫|JavaScript函式庫]]。Lodash的目的是透過[[函数式编程|函式語言程式設計]]的模式提供開發者常用的函式。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://github.com/lodash/lodash/wiki/FP-Guide|author=Lodash|title=Lodash Functional Programming Guide|accessdate=2020-07-24|archive-date=2021-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121183306/https://github.com/lodash/lodash/wiki/FP-Guide|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 概覽 ==

Lodash是基於'''Underscore.js'''的[[分叉_(软件开发)|分叉]]，其許多函式與功能與Underscore.js相似。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://blog.semmle.com/lodash-vs-underscore/|author=Albert Ziegler|title=Lodash vs Underscore: Dash of the titans|date=2017-10-26|website=Semmle Official Blog, a Github/Microsoft Company|accessdate=2020-07-24|archive-date=2020-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200724231554/https://blog.semmle.com/lodash-vs-underscore/|dead-url=no}}</ref>Underscore.js的創辦人是同為[[CoffeeScript|CoffeeScript]]的創辦人{{tsl|en|Jeremy Ashkenas|Jeremy Ashkenas}}。許多Underscore.js的開發人員也對Lodash的開發有所貢獻。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/by/jeremy-ashkenas|title=Jeremy Ashkenas Biography|author=Jeremy Ashkenas|website=New York Times|accessdate=2020-07-24|archive-date=2021-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112073913/https://www.nytimes.com/by/jeremy-ashkenas|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://github.com/underdash/underdash/issues/14|title=Underdash Github Issues: Lodash, underscore merge and usage discussion|website=Github|accessdate=2020-07-24|archive-date=2020-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201012052706/https://github.com/underdash/underdash/issues/14|dead-url=no}}</ref>

Lodash是目前在[[npm|npm]]上最多JavaScript軟體使用的開放原始碼[[軟體套件|軟體套件]]，每週下載次數三千三百萬次以上。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.npmjs.com/browse/depended|access-date=2020-07-24|title=npm most depended upon packages|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204120045/https://www.npmjs.com/browse/depended|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.npmjs.com/package/lodash|access-date=2020-07-24|title=lodash on npm|archive-date=2021-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204152937/https://www.npmjs.com/package/lodash|dead-url=no}}</ref>Lodash在開源軟體的廣泛使用讓此套件曾經成為[[依賴注入|依賴注入]]的[[漏洞|漏洞]]攻擊。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.zdnet.com/article/more-than-75-of-all-vulnerabilities-reside-in-indirect-dependencies/|title=More than 75% of all vulnerabilities reside in indirect dependencies|author=Catalin Cimpanu|date=2020-06-20|website=ZDNet|accessdate=2020-07-24|archive-date=2021-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119073001/https://www.zdnet.com/article/more-than-75-of-all-vulnerabilities-reside-in-indirect-dependencies/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://github.com/lodash/lodash/issues/4348|title=Lodash Github Issues: High severity vulnerability in 4.17.11|date=2019-07-02|website=Github|accessdate=2020-07-24|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111230049/https://github.com/lodash/lodash/issues/4348|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 範例 ==

Lodash包含[[陣列|陣列]]的[[排序算法|排序算法]]和過濾、[[集合_(计算机科学)|集合]]的演算法、數學函式、與字符串的變更函式，共包含超過一百個函式。<ref name="docs">{{Cite web|url=https://lodash.com/docs/|title=Lodash Docs|author=Lodash|accessdate=2020-07-23|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123162538/https://lodash.com/docs/|dead-url=no}}</ref>Lodash使用的[[函数式编程|函式語言程式設計]]模式允許開發者同時{{tsl|en|Method Chaining|串連}}多數個函式。比如，如果要同時排序和顛倒一個包含數字的陳列，可以使用以下[[句法|句法]]：<ref name="docs" />

<syntaxhighlight lang="javascript">
const _ = require('lodash')

const numbers = [2,5,4,3,1]
const sorted_numbers = _(numbers).sortBy().reverse().value();

// 結果: numbers = [5,4,3,2,1]
</syntaxhighlight>

